## Troubleshooting

### Common Issues

#### "command not found" errors

**Cause**: Tool not in PATH

**Solution**:
```bash
# Check PATH
bash .claude/plugins/foundation/skills/environment-setup/scripts/validate-path.sh --verbose

# Add to PATH in shell config
echo 'export PATH="/path/to/tool:$PATH"' >> ~/.bashrc
source ~/.bashrc
```

#### Version mismatch errors

**Cause**: Installed version doesn't meet requirements

**Solution**:
```bash
# Check version requirements
bash .claude/plugins/foundation/skills/environment-setup/scripts/validate-versions.sh

# Install correct version using version manager
nvm install {{NODE_VERSION}}  # for Node.js
pyenv install {{PYTHON_VERSION}}  # for Python
```

#### Permission denied errors

**Cause**: Missing permissions or need sudo

**Solution**:
```bash
# For Docker
sudo usermod -aG docker $USER
# Log out and back in

# For npm global packages
mkdir ~/.npm-global
npm config set prefix '~/.npm-global'
echo 'export PATH=~/.npm-global/bin:$PATH' >> ~/.bashrc
source ~/.bashrc
```

#### Environment variables not set

**Cause**: .env file missing or not loaded

**Solution**:
```bash
# Copy template
cp .env.example .env

# Edit values
nano .env

# Verify
bash .claude/plugins/foundation/skills/environment-setup/scripts/check-env-vars.sh
```

